// MARK: - Explore
"explore.greeting.hi" = "Hi,";
"explore.intro.data" = "Hi, last night your body entered a stable, relaxed, and highly restorative sleep state. From sleep onset rhythm to overnight structure, multiple key indicators were better than your recent average. This wasn’t just “a lucky good night,” but a night where your nervous system and sleep architecture worked in sync.";
"explore.intro.default" = "In every phase—falling asleep, waking up, and returning to deep sleep—Mindora keeps observing your sleep rhythm and adjusts how it stays with you. These insights aren’t just numbers; they come from the sleep scenes you use, the sound patterns, and the real feedback from your body.";
